The paper discusses the development of software tools for image and video annotation, which is a fundamental task in computer vision and multimedia information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely sub-categories include cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), as these fields are closely related to image and video annotation.
